  • Method Details

    • start

      public void start(javafx.stage.Stage mainStage, ArrayList<Album> albums, Photo added, Album original, boolean copy, boolean addition)
      Initializes the controller. Based on parameters, if in copy/move mode, it asks the user to input an existing album. In addition mode, it asks user for a valid name for a new album.
      Parameters:
      mainStage - for the Main Stage Window.
      albums - for the list of albums that a user has.
      added - for the Photo selected that user wants an operation performed on.
      original - for the album that the Photo selected originates in.
      copy - for the boolean that checks if the user prompts for a copy operation.
      addition - for the boolean that checks if the user prompts for a addition operation.
